sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as MiMo-Code Agent
    participant Provider as @ai-sdk/openai-compatible
    participant Server as Hono Server (server.ts)
    participant Converter as MessageConverter
    participant Adapter as DeepSeekWebAdapter
    participant Browser as BrowserManager
    participant Page as Playwright Page
    participant Web as DeepSeek Web Page

    Note over Agent,Web: === 非流式请求流程 ===

    Agent->>Provider: 1. 调用 languageModel
    Provider->>Server: 2. POST /v1/chat/completions { messages, stream: false }
    Server->>Server: 3. 解析/校验请求
    Server->>Converter: 4. convertMessages(messages)
    Converter->>Converter: 5. 合并 tool_call/tool_result 为自然语言
    Converter-->>Server: 6. 纯文本消息列表
    Server->>Adapter: 7. sendMessage(page, messages, { stream: false })
    Adapter->>Browser: 8. getSession(sessionId)
    Browser->>Page: 9. 获取/创建页面
    Page-->>Adapter: 10. 返回 Page 实例
    Adapter->>Page: 11. 清空输入框
    Adapter->>Page: 12. 输入最新消息文本
    Adapter->>Page: 13. 点击发送按钮
    Page->>Web: 14. 提交消息
    Web-->>Page: 15. 开始生成回复
    Adapter->>Page: 16. 等待回复完成 (poll DOM)
    Page-->>Adapter: 17. 完整回复文本
    Adapter-->>Server: 18. 返回完整文本 (含 reasoning_content)
    Server-->>Provider: 19. 200 OK { choices: [{ message: { content, reasoning_content } }] }
    Provider-->>Agent: 20. 返回 LanguageModelV3 响应

    Note over Agent,Web: === 流式 SSE 请求流程 ===

    Agent->>Provider: 21. 调用 languageModel (stream: true)
    Provider->>Server: 22. POST /v1/chat/completions { messages, stream: true }
    Server->>Converter: 23. convertMessages(messages)
    Converter-->>Server: 24. 纯文本消息列表
    Server->>Adapter: 25. sendMessage(page, messages, { stream: true })
    Adapter->>Browser: 26. getSession(sessionId)
    Browser->>Page: 27. 获取/创建页面
    Page-->>Adapter: 28. 返回 Page 实例
    Adapter->>Page: 29. 清空输入框
    Adapter->>Page: 30. 输入最新消息
    Adapter->>Page: 31. 点击发送按钮
    Page->>Web: 32. 提交消息
    Server->>Server: 33. 设置 SSE headers
    Server-->>Provider: 34. SSE 连接建立

    loop 思考内容增量提取
        Adapter->>Page: 35. MutationObserver 监听 DOM
        Page-->>Adapter: 36. 增量 thinking_content
        Adapter-->>Server: 37. yield delta
        Server-->>Provider: 38. SSE: data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"reasoning_content":"..."}}]}
    end

    loop 回复内容增量提取
        Adapter->>Page: 39. 监听回复容器变化
        Page-->>Adapter: 40. 增量 content
        Adapter-->>Server: 41. yield delta
        Server-->>Provider: 42. SSE: data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"content":"..."}}]}
    end

    Web-->>Page: 43. 回复完成
    Adapter-->>Server: 44. 迭代结束
    Server-->>Provider: 45. SSE: data: [DONE]
    Provider-->>Agent: 46. 流式合并完成

    Note over Agent,Web: === 消息格式转换流程 ===

    Server->>Converter: convertMessages(rawMessages)
    Note over Converter: 输入: [{role:"user", content:"你好"}, {role:"assistant", content:"好的", tool_calls:[...]}, {role:"tool", content:"结果"}]
    Converter->>Converter: 遍历 + 合并 tool_call/tool_result 对
    Note over Converter: 输出: [{role:"user", content:"你好"}, {role:"assistant", content:"好的"}, {role:"user", content:"[工具结果] 结果"}]
    Converter-->>Server: 转换后的纯文本消息列表
